<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/224143-i-have-read-he-book-awhile-ago-but-i-ve">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/224143-i-have-read-he-book-awhile-ago-but-i-ve">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
