<span id="freeTextContainer14974724788777031509">One of my most favourite books to this day. I need to re-read this one. It really fit the time of my life, which was difficult for me and in a way, the book helped me to cope. I don&apos;t know if that&apos;s the reason why I liked it so much or not. So, time to re-read it, I guess. To see where the book really stands.</span>
  <span id="freeText14974724788777031509" style="display:none">One of my most favourite books to this day. I need to re-read this one. It really fit the time of my life, which was difficult for me and in a way, the book helped me to cope. I don't know if that's the reason why I liked it so much or not. So, time to re-read it, I guess. To see where the book really stands.</span>
